# newdoc id = texts/birchbark/043
# date_created = 1380-1400
# transl_ru = От Бориса к Настасье. Как придет эта грамота, пришли мне человека на жеребце, потому что у меня здесь дел много. Да пришли рубашку — рубашку забыл.
# transl_en_1 = From Boris to Nastas’ia. As soon as this birch-bark (gramota) arrives, send me a person mounted on a stallion, since I have much to do here. And also send me a shirt – I forgot the shirt.
# transl_en_2 = From Boris to Nastas’ja. As soon as this letter arrives, send me a man on a stallion, because I have a lot of work here. And send a shirt; I forgot a shirt.
